<h2 id="instructions">Instructions</h2>

<p>Write a script that inputs a line of encrypted text and a distance value and outputs plaintext using a Caesar cipher.</p>

<p>The script should work for any printable characters.</p>

<p>An example of the program input and output is shown below:</p>

<div class="language-text highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Enter the coded text: Lipps${svph%
Enter the distance value: 4

Hello world!
</code></pre></div></div>

